<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="with=device-with, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>

    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-1BmE4kWBq78iYhFldvKuhfTAU6auU8tT94WrHftjDbrCEXSU1oBoqyl2QvZ6jIW3" crossorigin="anonymous">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="input-group mb-3">
        <label class="input-group-text" for="inputGroupSelect01">Select Query</label>
        <select class="form-select" id="inputGroupSelect01">
            <option selected>Query...</option>
            <option value="1">a) List country and city names whose PM 2.5 values are greater than 50 in 2015.</option>
            <option value="2">b) Calculate the AVG(PM 2.5) by country (show the results in a decreasing order).</option>
            <option value="3">c) Given a <country_input> from the user, show a historical PM 2.5 values by year.</option>
            <option value="4">d) Given a <year_input> and an input of <color_pm25> level of health concern from the user, calculate a total of the affected population (in number).</option>
        </select>
    </div>

    <div class="d-grid gap-2 d-md-flex justify-content-md-end">
        <button class="btn btn-primary me-md-2" type="button">Run</button>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-ka7Sk0Gln4gmtz2MlQnikT1wXgYsOg+OMhuP+IlRH9sENBO0LRn5q+8nbTov4+1p" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
